[03:11.48]	Hail, King of Scotland!
[03:15.88]ALL	Hail, King of Scotland!
[03:20.28]	[Flourish]
[03:22.17]MALCOLM	We shall not spend a large expense of time
[03:29.87]	Before we reckon with your several loves,
[03:37.26]	And make us even with you. My thanes and kinsmen,
[03:45.75]	Henceforth be earls, the first that ever Scotland
[03:54.40]	In such an honour named. What's more to do,
[04:01.94]	Which would be planted newly with the time,
